     C* F21: secondary file with NO match fields. Primary drains fully
     C* (vals 1,2,3 -> 6), then secondary (vals 10,20 -> 30). RPGRET=36.
     FSNPRIM  IP  F    80              DISK
     FSNSC    IS  F    80              DISK
     ISNPRIM      01
     I                                        1   20PVAL
     ISNSC        02
     I                                        1   20SVAL
     C  01                 ADD  PVAL      RPGRET
     C  02                 ADD  SVAL      RPGRET
     CLR                   SETOF
